title: Dorm Room Dilemma: How Students Retrieve Belongings from Campus
text: "We need to do this retrieval process in a very condensed way and the most orderly way for us to do that is for us to organize the process instead of bringing lots of people in," says President Hillary Link. "We're talking about 1700 plus people, plus whoever they bring with them help pack, it's a lot of people."
meta_description: Allegheny College explains plan to get students back their dorm room belongings, some students have concerns.
